hile maintaining site-specific customization options.",[5255],{"type":149,"attrs":5256},{"color":1233},{"type":69,"attrs":5258,"content":5259},{"level":138,"textAlign":139},[5260],{"text":4268,"type":75,"marks":5261},[5262,5264],{"type":149,"attrs":5263},{"color":1233},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":5266,"content":5267},{"textAlign":139},[5268,5273,5279],{"text":5269,"type":75,"marks":5270},"The evidence is clear: ",[5271],{"type":149,"attrs":5272},{"color":1233},{"text":5274,"type":75,"marks":5275},"yard operation efficiency comparison",[5276,5278],{"type":149,"attrs":5277},{"color":1233},{"type":710},{"text":5280,"type":75,"marks":5281}," shows that modern Yard Management Systems save a lot of time compared to traditional check-in processes. ",[5282],{"type":149,"attrs":5283},{"color":1233},{"type":112,"attrs":5285,"content":5286},{"textAlign":139},[5287],{"text":5288,"type":75,"marks":5289},"You've seen how automation can:",[5290],{"type":149,"attrs":5291},{"color":1233},{"type":1344,"content":5293},[5294,5305,5316],{"type":1347,"content":5295},[5296],{"type":112,"attrs":5297,"content":5298},{"textAlign":139},[5299],{"text":5300,"type":75,"marks":5301}," Reduce gate processing times by up to 85%",[5302,5304],{"type":149,"attrs":5303},{"color":1233},{"type":710},{"type":1347,"content":5306},[5307],{"type":112,"attrs":5308,"content":5309},{"textAlign":139},[5310],{"text":5311,"type":75,"marks":5312}," Improve dock throughput by over 50%",[5313,5315],{"type":149,"attrs":5314},{"color":1233},{"type":710},{"type":1347,"content":5317},[5318],{"type":112,"attrs":5319,"content":5320},{"textAlign":139},[5321],{"text":5322,"type":75,"marks":5323},"Cut asset search time by 90%.",[5324,5326],{"type":149,"attrs":5325},{"color":1233},{"type":710},{"type":112,"attrs":5328,"content":5329},{"textAlign":139},[5330],{"text":5331,"type":75,"marks":5332},"Traditional manual methods—with their paperwork, phone calls, and communication gaps—simply can't match the speed and accuracy o